README
------
This is the alpha2 release of the HDF5 format checker. This one is for the
HDF5 File Format Specification Version 1.1.

tool/ holds the source code of the h5check tool.
test/ holds the test suite of the h5check tool.
doc/  holds all document related to the tool

========
To build:
========
Assuming cc and h5cc are in your $PATH, just do
    % make
If you want to use a different C compiler and/or h5cc command, do
    % make CC=gcc H5CC=mypath/h5cc
    
============
To run tests:
============
    % make check

==========
To install:
==========
    % cp tool/h5check /usr/local/bin/h5check	# or wherever you choose to.

===================
Platforms supported:
===================
Linux 2.6
Being ported: AIX 5.3, Linux 2.4, Solaris 10.

========
Question:
========
Email help@hdfgroup.org.

